snippet.title: Lateche Norris Missing in San Diego. BF Joey Smith Not Talking & Has a Very Dark Past
snippet.description:
Lateche Norris Missing in San Diego. BF Joey Smith Not Talking & Has a Very Dark Past

Lateche Norris is 20-years old and has not been seen or heard from since November 5th, 2021 after traveling to San Diego, CA to be with her boyfriend, Joey Smith. Joey Smith will not answer questions despite logging into social media. Let's break it down...
